reviews.text: The store sells a lot of organic and imported products. The desire to try many things is high with resistance on the price tag. There is a small cafe in the store which makes very healthy food including veggie burger for lunch. Will definitely stop by to try it next time.
Quite pleasing shopping experience. Like the overall shop minimalist layout and interior design, the moto of the company and their staff service quality.
Love the environment and the concept of the store, good quality and very friendly prices on all recycled goods and vegan foods. Support any environmental friendly business.

large variety of ingredients and utensils. 
 the discount was calculated wrongly, 70%off was marked but 30% off was given at checkout. Since there was no receipt, there is no way to check the total amount, you better add up the total yourself before going to the cashier.

When it first opened I gave it 5 stars as they promoted less waste by giving discounts if you bring your own containers. 

They stopped that policy and now it is pretty much like any other store.

result.name: Slowood

reviews.text:
[堅尼地城。蔬食。素食]🍜🍜🍜
素菜版 omakase，給予的驚喜。
在味道，手工製作，質地以及心思。
八品
冷盤x3，熱盤x4，甜品
這個素食沒有蒜，五辛或蛋。 甜品的雪糕也是用豆奶製的。
巧妙運用了海藻、海苔、腐乳、生椒等刺激味覺。
洋甘菊加入冰塊之中，用於前菜上帶有陣陣的洋甘菊味道。
一邊食一邊跟朋友說，我們需要介紹給其他喜歡素食的朋友。
晚餐280元
店舖現正重整餐單，需留意他們的通告才知道什麼時候重開，有幸在最後一天試了這麼特別的omakase，真是幸運

店裡以白色和木塊為主調，這大概就是「森林系」吧 🤣 濃濃的自然味道，很喜歡！非常多純素產品，例如有純素蛋等， 還有很多好看耐用的生活用品呢！而且最近還新開了素咖啡館，我吃了純素小旦糕，鬆鬆軟軟，不錯喔~
The store is full of white and wooden blocks. This is probably called the "forest style". 🤣 I like the nature style very much! A lot of vegan products, such as vegan eggs...  There are many beautiful and durable daily necessities too! And a new veggie cafe just opened a few months ago, I tried a vegan cake, very soft and delicious, like!

visit date: 2019-03
細緻地劃分每一樣嘅商品,尤其是嗰啲散件冇包裝嘅,就更加小心咁掛起唔同容量嘅紙袋,方便顧客選購.因為店舖樓底高,唔會覺得有壓迫感,亦都唔會有好多店員四圍行/監視你嘅感覺.
來了試佢地個 tasting menu, 真心好食，不過等候上菜速度就真係非常離譜，起碼 15-20 鐘先上一道菜，我同屋企人等到非常不耐煩。七點十分入席，九點十五分先完，暫時不會考慮推薦呢間餐廳...

The store sells a lot of organic and imported products. The desire to try many things is high with resistance on the price tag. There is a small cafe in the store which makes very healthy food including veggie burger for lunch. Will definitely stop by to try it next time.
